# HotelAI Architecture

`docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` is the source of truth. Read it before changing routes, feature structure, services, mutations, shared types, or reusable UI patterns.

Keep this rule short. Do not copy architecture details here.

## Non-Negotiables

- `app/**/page.tsx` stays thin: fetch data, wrap in `AppShell`, pass props.
- Feature UI lives under `components/dashboard/<feature>/`.
- Reads go in `lib/services/*.service.ts`; writes go in `lib/services/*.mutations.ts`.
- Domain types live in `types/`.
- `components/ui/` remains generic UI primitives only.
- Auth + tenant context comes from `lib/tenant.ts` (`getCurrentHotelId`, `requireUser`); `/login` is the only public route (guarded by `proxy.ts`).
